data.description:
This home features so much space! 3 bedrooms located on the main floor. Laundry on the same level! Beautiful open kitchen. Large living room. The basement has so much room to do with whatever you like! There is another bathroom in the basement that isn't quite finished, but ready to make it your own. There is an additional laundry room in the basement. Covered back patio, great for sipping lemonade on a hot day. Attached 2 car garage for parking and an additional detached 2 car garage in the back could be used for additional parking, a work shop or whatever your imagination comes up with. Additional garage is locked for the time being.
